                    <p class="color-black">Please note that this change does not affect your account or access to the workspace. All data and files within the workspace will remain intact, and you will continue to have the same level of access and permissions as before . </p>
                        
                    <p class="color-black">If you have any questions or concerns about this changes , please do not hesitate to reach out to us . We appreciate your continued support and look forward to working with you in the future .  .</p>
                    <p class="color-black">Best Regards </p>
                    <p class="color-black"><b>Reetesh Yadav</b></p>
